Version 1.1 Info
May 22, 2014
Released under Mozilla Public License, version 2.0 About this Add-on
An extension to simplify the use of Twitch.tv directly from Firefox. All games on Twitch.tv are supported. A search function allows finding of other games and streamers. A dedicated favourites view encompasses all games and shows all favourites together.I am actively developing this addon - Leave improvement suggestions below and you might see them in a new version. Alternatively, let me know what doesn't work!Enjoying the addon? I accept Bitcoin donations! BTC: 1LPbKVNGFM2XyFr2r8UryLm8v9irobA9FqDOGE: DMayK6NbqDuLcTTwxfwzKDsFZT98C3n6rGReal money is also greatly appreciated!
Version Information
Version 1.1
Released May 22, 2014
132.9 kB
Works with
Firefox 21.0 and later - Improved scrolling event handling (Hopefully fixed the bug!)- Hidden manual "more" links- Alternate names in popup- Importing of favourites from Twitch support
Source code released under Mozilla Public License, version 2.0 What's this?
